 & =\left\Vert \frac{-\mu b+\mu a}{1-\mu}\right\Vert =\left|\mu\right|\left\Vert \frac{a-b}{1-\mu}+b-b\right\Vert \\
 & =\mu\left\Vert \frac{a-b+b-\mu b}{1-\mu}-b\right\Vert =\mu\left\Vert \frac{a-\mu b}{1-\mu}-b\right\Vert \\
 & =\mu\left\Vert y-b\right\Vert \leq\mu\left\Vert y-b\right\Vert 
